00:01:21.079 --> 00:01:23.429
box of them."We're going to take

00:01:23.439 --> 00:01:24.710
this

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.950
communion and believe God

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:29.990
today for everything you need. I believe

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.069
