00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:55.150
Jesus. We thank You, Lord, for

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:58.189
it. Lord,

00:04:58.189 --> 00:04:58.199
I

00:04:58.199 --> 00:05:01.350
