00:44:33.200 --> 00:44:35.309
he said,

00:44:35.319 --> 00:44:42.910
"It is written,

00:44:46.280 --> 00:44:48.870
devil."He

00:44:51.880 --> 00:44:55.670
wasn't moved.

00:45:00.200 --> 00:45:01.910
Stand

00:45:04.359 --> 00:45:08.150
steadfast like a solid pillar.

00:45:08.160 --> 00:45:11.309
My house is built upon the Rock.

00:45:11.319 --> 00:45:14.230
When the

00:45:14.240 --> 00:45:16.630
storms of life come, they don't knock down

00:45:16.640 --> 00:45:19.790
my house. My house is built on

00:45:19.800 --> 00:45:22.390
a firm foundation.

00:45:36.280 --> 00:45:39.710
The name of

00:45:39.720 --> 00:45:42.670
the Lord

00:45:42.680 --> 00:45:45.150
is a strong tower, and the righteous run

00:45:45.160 --> 00:45:49.030
to it and are

00:45:49.040 --> 00:45:52.349
safe. That's what we stand on

00:45:52.359 --> 00:45:54.870
today. No matter

00:45:54.870 --> 00:45:54.880
the

00:45:54.880 --> 00:45:57.430
drama in the news,

00:45:57.440 --> 00:46:01.309
we're not moved by it. We

00:46:01.319 --> 00:46:04.349
take our authority over the nations,

00:46:04.359 --> 00:46:07.109
our area,

00:46:07.119 --> 00:46:09.710
our house, and our town. We

00:46:09.720 --> 00:46:11.470
pray over our government

00:46:11.470 --> 00:46:11.480
and

00:46:11.480 --> 00:46:13.390
leadership. We thank You, Lord, that

00:46:13.390 --> 00:46:13.400
on

00:46:13.400 --> 00:46:16.670
Inauguration Day, there will be no

00:46:16.680 --> 00:46:19.710
disruptions or distractions; it will

00:46:19.720 --> 00:46:23.510
be a time of great

00:46:23.520 --> 00:46:27.829
peace. They will not assassinate

00:46:27.839 --> 00:46:31.270
Trump; they will not hurt him. A thousand shall

00:46:31.280 --> 00:46:33.790
fall at his side and ten thousand at his right

00:46:33.790 --> 00:46:33.800
hand,

00:46:33.800 --> 00:46:36.349
but it will not come nigh him. We pray over

00:46:36.349 --> 00:46:36.359
JD

00:46:36.359 --> 00:46:39.510
Vance; no weapon formed

00:46:39.520 --> 00:46:42.030
against these people will prosper. Thank

00:46:42.040 --> 00:46:45.750
You, Father, for Your hand over

00:46:45.760 --> 00:46:49.190
all his

00:46:49.200 --> 00:46:51.430
cabinet.

00:46:54.400 --> 00:46:57.230
Thank you for

00:46:57.240 --> 00:46:59.349
joining me today.

00:47:03.640 --> 00:47:06.109
We'll be back again tomorrow.

00:47:06.119 --> 00:47:07.750
Tomorrow will

00:47:07.750 --> 00:47:07.760
be

00:47:07.760 --> 00:47:11.069
day 51.

00:47:11.079 --> 00:47:13.190
I appreciate you

00:47:13.190 --> 00:47:13.200
all

00:47:13.200 --> 00:47:16.349
